title: PLat 5 top/jungle lf team or a duo partner.
body:
Add me in game if you have a spot available or any questions.

Metaalz.

replies.body:
Hi, would you be interested in joining my ranked team as the top laner? We are currently in silver 5 but have only played 8 games, so I feel we could easily get to gold. We usually practice at about 10:30 AEST almost every night. We currently have a play 5 adc, plat 3 jgler, gold 4 mid laner so we aren't trash.
Thanks for your time :)
-Traloop
asking a plat to join a silver v team? cute
